Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:15.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}本当に現実なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:20.31,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}心がまだ追いついて来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.65,0:22:23.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}今は想像出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:28.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}この先押し寄せる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.28,0:22:32.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}Still,I have to keep going this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:34.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}あなたが居ない世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:36.25,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}miss you so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:39.96,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}消えないこの鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.38,0:22:43.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}会いたいあの笑顔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:49.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}もう一度近づきたい話したい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:52.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1}I know life can be so hard.
