Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.57,0:23:15.95,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}奉獻給你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.45,0:23:22.29,EDCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur1\bord0.8\c&HFAE7FB&\3c&HBD36C2&\4c&HB75AC3&}是時候與你說再見了
